en.answer:
Both cards will be sent to the Graveyard normally, and will not be banished.

(This outcome does not depend on whether the card remains treated as a Trap.)
en.question: Different Dimension Ground has previously resolved this turn. If a Conquistador of the Golden Land that has been Special Summoned as a monster by its effect, or a The Phantom Knights of Shade Brigandine that has been Special Summoned as a monster by its effect, would be sent to the Graveyard, will these cards be banished by Different Dimension Ground?
en.title: If a Trap Card that's been Special Summoned as a monster is sent to the Graveyard during a turn in which Different Dimension Ground resolved, will it be banished?

ja.answer:
除外されずに墓地へ送られます。

（モンスターゾーンで罠カードとして扱われているかどうかによって、結果が異なることはありません。）
